  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nI have royally fucked up all of my migrations - i want to  just run tests against local ganache WITHOUT my deploy scripts being called. I wish there was a way to force truffle test to NEVER run deploy scripts. \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nfuck up a bunch of deployments then try to run some tests\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nif i am only calling .new() in my test scripts, truffle should NOT try to run my migrations. \r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\ntruffle wants to run my migrations \r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: \r\n* Ethereum client: any\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): latest\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 14\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`):  any\r\n",
